HOW TO PREPARE A REAL DEVICE INSTALLER:
---------------------------------------
This Cfx Companion Web App can be wrapped into a production-grade native Android APK in minutes using Apache Cordova, Capacitor, or a Progressive Web App (PWA) wrapper:

1. CAPACITOR WRAPPER METHOD:
   $ npm install @capacitor/core @capacitor/cli
   $ npx cap init "Cfx Companion" "com.cfx.offline" --web-dir=dist
   $ npm install @capacitor/android
   $ npx cap add android
   $ npm run build
   $ npx cap sync
   $ npx cap open android (This will open Android Studio where you can hit Build APK!)

2. PWA INSTALL METHOD:
   Simply open this development URL inside Google Chrome or Microsoft Edge on your Android handset, swipe up, and click "Add to Home Screen". The Web APK will generate automatically and run as a standalone fullscreen game overlay!

